data.description: This great home features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and a spacious 1673 sq.ft. of living space. Step inside to the formal living area and dining space or this space would be perfect for a sitting area. The large kitchen has loads of counter space and storage. Refrigerator, range, built-in microwave and a breakfast bar for casual dining. Laundry room is just off the kitchen and washer and dryer are included. The split floor plan affords privacy with the primary suite away from the other bedrooms. Master bath features a separate tub and shower, double sinks, walk-in closet and linen closet. Brand new inverter HVAC system with electronic filters! Water heater is 1.5 years old. This property also offers RV parking making it convenient to store your RV on-site. Solar system provides owner with electr ic bill credit of $96 per month on average.
